00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:08.760
SEM SAÍDA

107
00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:19.133
As chaves.

108
00:08:24.432 --> 00:08:26.461
Um dia de cada vez,
certo, Mikey?


109
00:08:45.717 --> 00:08:48.175
CENTRO DE REABILITAÇÃO
